| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5128 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8743c7af-e9f3-51f3-8715-1cd19ff9db67"
